subject: Class not found Error
msgSnippet: Hi, I am starting to use Junit for my new project. Am getting the following error while running, Class not found com: client
messageBody:
Hi,

Am getting the following error while running,

Java.lang.Classnot foundException.com.clientname.Projectname.DAO.

Let me know if query needs some more information.


Thank you and Regards,
Sowmya.
